    %section
      %h2 What is CSS3 Sass mixins?
      
      %p 
        :markdown 
          Similar to [CSS3 Please!](http://css3please.com), this util makes it easier to use css3 in our daily projects by letting "someone else" managing vendor prefixes and (nasty) IE filters. 
      %p 
        :markdown
          CSS3 Sass Mixins is for minimalistics only. A way more feature-rich and qualified way of dealing with CSS3 is to use [Compass](http://compasstyle.org).
